  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feeling a bit bored at work? <i>Come fishing!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fishing On My Desktop is an idle fishing game that runs as a floating button on your desktop. Whether you’re working, studying, watching movies, or even playing other games, you can enjoy the fun of fishing at the same time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263340/extras/a4671d6de90e3ad6c8ce989ad1f51dc7.webp?t=1750935885\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263340/extras/a4671d6de90e3ad6c8ce989ad1f51dc7.poster.avif?t=1750935885\" class=\"bb_img\" width=549 height=100 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Interesting Fishing Experience</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just a click to start fishing—no complex controls needed.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fish in rivers, lakes, and oceans.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect over 100 different types of fish.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique rods and bait options.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some unexpected catches: crabs, pearls, jellyfish, message bottles, and even treasure chests…</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263340/extras/dc5f6549ca51f29149a024062db14aca.webp?t=1750935885\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263340/extras/dc5f6549ca51f29149a024062db14aca.poster.avif?t=1750935885\" class=\"bb_img\" width=549 height=100 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >And</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The cutest cat in the world.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 romanceable NPCs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30+ Steam achievements.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263340/extras/398bca7292208f1de2c26b4790807282.avif?t=1750935885\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263340/extras_big/398bca7292208f1de2c26b4790807282.avif?t=1750935885 width=800 height=331 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Come and experience the joy of desktop fishing!</p>",
